  <brief_title>Lipid Based Food Additives for Treating Patients With Dry Mouth</brief_title>
  <official_title>Lipid Based Food Additives for Treating Patients With Dry Mouth</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hadassah Medical Organization</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hadassah Medical Organization</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Over 10% of adult population suffers from dry mouth (xerostomia). The aim of this double
      blind prospective clinical trial is to examine a new lipid based food additive formulation to
      ease mouth dryness in these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
